    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved! I'm happy to answer any questions or have you come by for a test drive. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
