    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this car is well-sorted: the rear subframe has been reinforced, and both the rod bearings and VANOS system have been serviced to ensure long-term reliability. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and feedback expected of the chassis. It shows honest wear consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle, offering a raw, analog driving experience without the need for immediate mechanical intervention.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
