      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The mechanical health is prioritized with a recently serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain chassis rigidity. It utilizes a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a refreshed suspension setup for optimal turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is exceptionally tight, offering the visceral feedback and 8,000 RPM redline that defines this generation. A well-sorted enthusiast machine with no deferred maintenance.",
